<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Alicia Silverstone, 'Hotel Rwanda' Hero Coming to UCF</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Mark Freeman
		
		<span class="date">January 13, 2011</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2384/en_US/aliciamain.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Courtesy of Alicia Silverstone</p>
			
			<p>Actress and activist Alicia Silverstone will speak at UCF Thursday, Feb. 3.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041052a2b5bb012d44907649006be3">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
